Stagecoach_Theatre_Arts http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stagecoach_Theatre_Arts 0 Stagecoach Theatre Arts Ltd is a professional part-time theatre arts school with over 600 schools in the United Kingdom. Training is offered in singing, dancing and acting. Stagecoach Theatre Arts is a franchise for part-time theatre arts schools in Australia, Canada, Germany, Gibraltar, Malta, Spain and the UK.
